<em>&quot;Why is this implying the Foundation is a work of fiction? Who signed off on this?&quot; — Researcher Rose Labelle</em><br />
<em>&quot;Is this supposed to be a Mary Sue thing? I didn't do any of that. I've never even met Bright.&quot; — Researcher Rose Labelle</em><br />
